---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Projects — Paul Kuo" description="在結構性問題中工作。" activePage="projects">
  <div class="section-container" style="padding-top:120px;">
    <header class="blog-hero">
      <h1 data-i18n="projects.title">Projects</h1>
      <p data-i18n="projects.subtitle">在結構性問題中工作。</p>
    </header>
    <div class="projects-grid">
      <article class="project-card circleflow">
        <div class="project-icon" style="background:rgba(5,150,105,0.1)">♻️</div>
        <h2 data-i18n="projects.circleflow.name">CircleFlow</h2>
        <div class="prose"><p data-i18n="projects.circleflow.desc">AI 驅動的循環經濟數據基礎設施。連結廢棄物產生者與資源化業者，用數據重建產業物質流的可見性與可信度。</p></div>
        <div class="project-tags"><span class="project-tag">循環再利用</span><span class="project-tag">AI</span><span class="project-tag">Platform</span><span class="project-tag">ESG</span></div>
        <div class="project-strategic"><strong>Structural Significance</strong><span data-i18n="projects.circleflow.significance">工業文明的線性模型正在耗盡它的物質基礎。CircleFlow 處理的不只是廢棄物媒合，而是重建「物質秩序」——讓資源的流向、價值與歸屬重新變得可追蹤、可信任、可治理。</span></div>
      </article>
      <article class="project-card sdti">
        <div class="project-icon" style="background:rgba(180,83,9,0.1)">🤝</div>
        <h2 data-i18n="projects.taiwan_japan.name">台日產業與技術整合</h2>
        <div class="prose"><p data-i18n="projects.taiwan_japan.desc">在製造、生醫技術、循環再利用與跨境貿易等領域推動台日合作。關注的不只是產業媒合，而是如何在不同制度與文化之間建立長期信任，讓技術與價值在更大的秩序中流動。</p></div>
        <div class="project-tags"><span class="project-tag">製造</span><span class="project-tag">生醫</span><span class="project-tag">循環再利用</span><span class="project-tag">跨境貿易</span><span class="project-tag">信任結構</span></div>
        <div class="project-strategic"><strong>Structural Significance</strong><span data-i18n="projects.taiwan_japan.significance">產業合作跨越國界時，障礙往往不在技術，而在制度、文化與風險認知的差異。這項工作處理的是信任秩序——如何在不同文明語境中建立可持續的合作結構。</span></div>
      </article>
      <article class="project-card debate">
        <div class="project-icon" style="background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1)">🧠</div>
        <h2 data-i18n="projects.debate.name">多模型認知協作框架</h2>
        <div class="prose"><p data-i18n="projects.debate.desc">讓多個語言模型對同一議題進行結構化辯論與交叉驗證，建立比單一模型更可靠的認知基礎。</p></div>
        <div class="project-tags"><span class="project-tag">Multi-Agent</span><span class="project-tag">認知基礎設施</span></div>
        <div class="project-strategic"><strong>Structural Significance</strong><span data-i18n="projects.debate.significance">單一模型的輸出是觀點，多模型的碰撞才接近判斷。這個框架處理的是認知秩序——當資訊的生產速度遠超人類的處理能力，個體如何維持獨立思考與可靠決策的結構條件。</span></div>
      </article>
      <article class="project-card brand">
        <div class="project-icon" style="background:rgba(220,38,38,0.1)">📡</div>
        <h2 data-i18n="projects.brand.name">跨平台內容基礎設施</h2>
        <div class="prose"><p data-i18n="projects.brand.desc">當話語權被演算法壟斷，個體的獨立表達需要自己的基礎設施。</p></div>
        <div class="project-tags"><span class="project-tag">個體基礎設施</span><span class="project-tag">獨立發聲</span></div>
        <div class="project-strategic"><strong>Structural Significance</strong><span data-i18n="projects.brand.significance">話語秩序正在被平台與演算法重新分配。這個基礎設施處理的問題是：一個人如何在不依賴任何單一平台的前提下，維持思想輸出的獨立性與持續性。</span></div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
